{"tid":1775024,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭若驊稱辭職報道無根據 不評論丈夫公司遭競委會調查","createTime":"2019-12-08T14:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T16:39:50.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b151c25ab4d0234ce1b8c31eadd7876444dc63","tid":1775024,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》報道引述3名知情人士指，律政司司長鄭若驊原本想請辭並留在倫敦，但北京下令她回港。鄭若驊透過新聞秘書回覆表示，鄭若驊沒有如報道所指提出請辭，指有關報道全無事實根據。《金融時報》提到鄭若驊返港後不久，其丈夫潘樂陶旗下的安樂工程發公告，指競爭事務委員會人員到其全資附屬公司調查。鄭若驊透過新聞秘書回覆，表示報道提及的案件正由競委會調查，律政司司長不適宜作出任何評論，但鄭若驊對報道所提及的公司並沒有實益股份，亦沒有參與該公司的運作。鄭若驊上月訪問英國倫敦，被示威者包圍期間跌倒，她在英國接受手術後到北京接受檢查，上周二回港。她當時表示，中國駐英大使館安排她往北京就醫。<br />\n<br />\n2019-12-08 22:49:09"},{"pid":"01071adcba6018576fea268bb11e905f75319085","tid":1775024,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"覆得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc0a20a1b409f3f9e6d1f93e04576dc36c441ea","tid":1775024,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01071adcba6018576fea268bb11e905f75319085","tid":1775024,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"覆得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:55:57.000Z","msg":"因為唔係佢本人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115f29245d26e33f2ff5fccf6ae720c79aa047e2","tid":1775024,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"黨給你說嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想妳同老公安全就要靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe088218b638eeaaff4ef1289ef4f29ac4a32ba4","tid":1775024,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"一定話無根據啦<br />\n唔通話係呀 <br />\n我俾人迫嫁 俾人夾返首都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c04b31e8e79b0b11865531c507759f514caace","tid":1775024,"uid":189145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:57:31.000Z","msg":"Ⅳ級小說，靚仔莫看<br />\n波華，前輩級AV女星，與波多野結衣，蒼井空等齊名，因胸前偉大及做野不錫身，廣受宅男献精。特别是其埋身絕技，含吹瀨啜嗦，抛篩磨擰揈， 拗彈摺刮擢，吸夾撬插隊，無人能及。但因年老色衰，且心囗矽袋硬化變型，故欲自資自導新片駁反彈。片名&ldquo;送中法&rdquo;，全名是&ldquo;姣婆送穴中出有辦法&rdquo;。惟因出手過低，新一輩AV女星如三上悠亞，川上奈奈美等厭對手黑鬼過於粗大，且要撥穴中出，太下賤超越人類道德底線拒演。波華為免血本無歸，唯有親自上馬演出。<br />\n詩云 ：法皇自嘗獨創斷頭台，波華自編導演送中法。"},{"pid":"fc24cd2bd7bbf3a7857e323913d124e88ae8a1eb","tid":1775024,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借個位<br />\n<br />\n【英國戰線】大選民調：遊離票極多，大家齊拉票，平權機會增<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1774061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1774061</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPABEHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPABEHT.png&h=3842ea33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AcXo9y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AcXo9y.png&h=0af33bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sO1ECuz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsO1ECuz.png&h=fe6a1661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kpHHAgf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkpHHAgf.png&h=542864ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5d066842bb2f9ac56113c6c22063afc4aa1c5ef","tid":1775024,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01071adcba6018576fea268bb11e905f75319085","tid":1775024,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"覆得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /